To help Her cross all the centers properly, you put your right hand

01:22:18.652 --> 01:22:22.412
on the left hand side of your stomach, in the upper part

01:22:22.992 --> 01:22:29.632
- [INTERPRETER]

01:22:29.892 --> 01:22:35.592
- [INTERPRETER]
- Here, with full confidence,

01:22:36.432 --> 01:22:41.932
please say ten times, "Mother, I am my own master,

01:22:42.192 --> 01:22:49.592
I am my own guru, I am my guide," say this ten times.

01:22:50.152 --> 01:22:55.252
[INTERPRETER]

01:22:55.452 --> 01:22:58.932
[INTERPRETER]

01:23:30.672 --> 01:23:34.672
Now, raise your hand on your heart

01:23:35.712 --> 01:23:42.772
- [INTERPRETER]
- and here, we have to see the greatest truth

01:23:43.692 --> 01:23:50.172
- [INTERPRETER]
- so now, with full confidence in yourself

01:23:50.692 --> 01:23:56.392
please say, "Mother, I am the Spirit." Please say twelve times.

01:23:57.132 --> 01:24:03.032
[INTERPRETER]

01:24:31.812 --> 01:24:36.992
Now, we have to know that the Divine is the ocean and love,

01:24:37.352 --> 01:24:40.872
ocean of love and Grace

01:24:41.252 --> 01:24:46.552
[INTERPRETER]

01:24:46.792 --> 01:24:51.212
but above all, it is the ocean of forgiveness

01:24:51.892 --> 01:24:56.392
[INTERPRETER]

01:24:56.872 --> 01:25:04.032
and whatever mistakes you commit, is capable of completely neutralizing it.

01:25:04.832 --> 01:25:11.052
[INTERPRETER]

01:25:11.272 --> 01:25:15.912
So, have faith in the power of forgiveness of the Divine.

01:25:16.172 --> 01:25:19.552
[INTERPRETER]

01:25:20.472 --> 01:25:26.812
So, raise your right hand in the corner

01:25:27.552 --> 01:25:33.192
of your shoulder and your neck and place your right hand,

01:25:33.832 --> 01:25:40.252
- head towards the right.
