01:26:07.772 --> 01:26:15.212
[INTERPRETER]

01:26:15.732 --> 01:26:21.032
- You should be pleasantly placed towards yourself
- [INTERPRETER]

01:26:21.692 --> 01:26:27.192
- because you're entering into the kingdom of God.
- [INTERPRETER]

01:26:28.392 --> 01:26:33.372
So now, say it sixteen times, "I am not at all guilty."

01:26:33.732 --> 01:26:37.232
[INTERPRETER]

01:26:41.332 --> 01:26:46.272
Now, raise your right hand to your forehead, across.

01:26:47.112 --> 01:26:52.492
- [INTERPRETER]
- Put your left hand towards Me.

01:26:52.752 --> 01:26:58.352
- [INTERPRETER]
- Now, press on both the sides.

01:26:58.612 --> 01:27:06.672
- [INTERPRETER]
- On this center you have to say, "Mother, I forgive everyone."

01:27:07.492 --> 01:27:11.632
- [INTERPRETER]

01:27:12.232 --> 01:27:16.972
- Now, some people think, it's difficult
- [INTERPRETER]

01:27:17.252 --> 01:27:22.872
- but it is a myth, whether you forgive or don't forgive
- [INTERPRETER]

01:27:23.472 --> 01:27:27.912
but if you do not forgive, then you play into wrong hands.

01:27:28.552 --> 01:27:32.952
[INTERPRETER]

01:27:33.192 --> 01:27:36.692
- So, from your heart you have to say, not how many times,

01:27:37.212 --> 01:27:41.192
[INTERPRETER]

01:27:42.532 --> 01:27:46.152
- "I forgive everyone."
- [INTERPRETER]

01:27:46.672 --> 01:27:52.572
- Now, take your hand on your back side
- [INTERPRETER]

01:27:53.052 --> 01:27:59.432
and put your head on that and put the load of your head, slowly,

01:28:00.132 --> 01:28:04.232
[INTERPRETER]

