01:28:20.192 --> 01:28:28.172
[INTERPRETER]

01:28:31.552 --> 01:28:37.772
- Now, please stretch your hand, right hand
- [INTERPRETER]

01:28:38.212 --> 01:28:46.052
- left hand towards Me
- [INTERPRETER]
